**Note**: This context focuses on native/systems code vulnerabilities from the CWE/SANS Top 25. Many entries (injection, hardcoded credentials, path traversal) overlap with OWASP Top 10 but manifest differently in C/C++. Use with `security-review.context` for general OWASP framing.
